# Production backend URL — REPLACE before building an APK for distribution.
# Point this to your publicly deployed FastAPI backend (Railway / Render / Fly.io / etc.)
# The value is baked into the APK at build time and cannot be changed after.
#
# Example:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=https://aan-backend.up.railway.app
EXPO_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=https://your-backend-domain.example.com
